Note: Debug and Performance Monitoring Functions
Process called "create_dsl_debug_tracer" returns DSLDebugTracer:
    Return DSLDebugTracer with:
        trace_level as "info"
        trace_output as list containing
        dsl_events as list containing
        metadata as dictionary containing

Process called "create_dsl_performance_monitor" returns DSLPerformanceMonitor:
    Return DSLPerformanceMonitor with:
        metrics as dictionary containing
        thresholds as dictionary containing:
            "dsl_registration_time" as 1.0
            "dsl_parsing_time" as 0.5
            "dsl_generation_time" as 1.0
            "dsl_validation_time" as 0.5
        alerts as list containing
        metadata as dictionary containing

Process called "get_dsl_trace" that takes support as DSLSupport returns List[DSLTraceEntry]:
    Return support.debug_tracer.trace_output

Process called "get_dsl_events" that takes support as DSLSupport returns List[DSLEvent]:
    Return support.debug_tracer.dsl_events

Process called "clear_dsl_trace" that takes support as DSLSupport:
    Set support.debug_tracer.trace_output to list containing
    Set support.debug_tracer.dsl_events to list containing

Process called "get_dsl_performance_metrics" that takes support as DSLSupport returns Dictionary[String, DSLPerformanceMetric]:
    Return support.performance_monitor.metrics

Process called "get_dsl_performance_alerts" that takes support as DSLSupport returns List[DSLPerformanceAlert]:
    Return support.performance_monitor.alerts

Process called "set_dsl_performance_threshold" that takes support as DSLSupport and metric as String and threshold as Float returns Boolean:
    Try:
        Set support.performance_monitor.thresholds[metric] to threshold
        Return true
        
    Catch error:
        Return false

Note: DSL Result Types
Type DSLParseResult is:
    | DSLParseSuccess with ast as ASTNode and tokens as List[Token] and metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]
    | DSLParseError with error as String and details as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type DSLGenerationResult is:
    | DSLGenerationSuccess with code as String and metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]
    | DSLGenerationError with error as String and details as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type DSLValidationResult is:
    | DSLValidationSuccess with ast as ASTNode and metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]
    | DSLValidationError with error as String and details as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type ErrorReporter is Dictionary with:
    reporter_id as String
    error_types as List[String]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any] 